帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Alex-Fine-Cassie-and-Diddy.-Credit-Tommaso-Boddi-Emma-McIntyre-and-Paras-Griffin-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="亚历克斯·法恩、卡西和迪迪。图片来源：Tommaso Boddi、Emma McIntyre 和 Paras Griffin，来自 GETTY" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Alex-Fine-Cassie-and-Diddy.-Credit-Tommaso-Boddi-Emma-McIntyre-and-Paras-Griffin-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Alex-Fine-Cassie-and-Diddy.-Credit-Tommaso-Boddi-Emma-McIntyre-and-Paras-Griffin-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Alex-Fine-Cassie-and-Diddy.-Credit-Tommaso-Boddi-Emma-McIntyre-and-Paras-Griffin-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Alex-Fine-Cassie-and-Diddy.-Credit-Tommaso-Boddi-Emma-McIntyre-and-Paras-Griffin-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Alex-Fine-Cassie-and-Diddy.-Credit-Tommaso-Boddi-Emma-McIntyre-and-Paras-Griffin-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Alex-Fine-Cassie-and-Diddy.-Credit-Tommaso-Boddi-Emma-McIntyre-and-Paras-Griffin-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Diddy">吹牛</a>老爹的前伴侣卡西的丈夫亚历克斯·法恩在袭击视频发生后给这位说唱大亨写了一封信。</p><p>迪迪（Diddy），真名肖恩·库姆斯（Sean Combs），目前正面临一系列有关性交易、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-accused-of-sexual-harassment-and-assault-by-music-producer-3593467">性侵犯和性骚扰</a>指控的持续调查。这位说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sean-diddy-combs-homes-raided-sex-trafficking-investigation-3609464">在迈阿密和洛杉矶的住所于三月份遭到突击搜查</a>，似乎与这些指控有关。</p><div id="playlist-player-jwplayer"><div class="playlist-player-container"><p>上周（3 月 17 日），美国有线电视新闻网 ( <a href="https://edition.cnn.com/2024/05/17/entertainment/sean-combs-cassie-ventura"><em>CNN</em></a> ) 获取并发布了一段视频，视频<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newly-published-surveillance-footage-reveals-diddy-attacking-cassie-3757408">显示这位说唱歌手殴打了他的前搭档、歌手卡西，</a>并从附近的桌子上向她投掷了一个不明物体。</p><p>此后，迪迪<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-apologises-for-inexcusable-2016-video-allegedly-showing-him-attacking-ex-cassie-3757559">为自己在视频中攻击卡西的“不可原谅”行为道歉</a>。</p><p>这段视频与<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cassie-accuses-sean-diddy-combs-rape-abuse-lawsuit-3542013">卡西在针对这位说唱大亨的诉讼中提供的证词</a>相符，她在诉讼中声称迪迪在酒店“喝得酩酊大醉，用拳头打了[她]的脸”，然后尾随她进入走廊，并向她扔玻璃花瓶。当他睡着时她试图离开。</p><p>现在，法恩（自 2019 年起成为卡西的丈夫）分享了一封公开信，声援他的妻子，谴责针对妇女和女孩的暴力行为，写道：“殴打女性的男人不是男人。能够实现这一目标并保护这些人的人不是男人。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C7FM_EoulZk/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g